      ******************************************************
** TB1(10A)
0 CANCEL
1 CHANGE
2 ADD
3 INQUIRY                                          JW7
** ER (60) ........2.........3.........4.........6
E-01 ENTER 0, 1, 2 OR 3 FOR UPDATE#
E-02 ENTER DELIVERY CODE !
E-03 DELIVERY CODE NOT FOUND !
E-04 DELIVERY CODE WAS CANCELLED !
E-05 DELIVERY CODE EXISTS !
E-06 ENTER LIST TYPE !
E-07 ENTER LIST TYPE 01 TO 10 !

E-09 LABEL TYPE <1=LAYOUT1 / 2=LAYOUT2 / 3=LAYOUT3>
E-10 ENTER # OF PACKING LIST !
E-11 ENTER # OF LABEL !
E-12 TRANSPORTATION WILL BE USED FOR CUSTOM SHEET
E-13 ENTER 01 OR 02 FOR CUSTOM SHEET TYPE !
E-14 COUNTRY SHOULD BE BLANK WHEN CUST = BLANK
E-15 ENTER COUNTRY !
E-16 INVALID MAX. BOXES OF PALLET !
E-17 CUSTOM SHEET TYPE SHOULD BE BLANK !
E-18 SUPPLIER FOR PRINT SHOULD NOT BE BLANK !
